    <div id="main-content">

        <h3>Hotel Features</h3>
        <div id="features-h-dots"><img src="images/spacer.gif" height="1" width="1" /></div>
        <div class="infobox" id="the-hotel-infobox">
            <h4>The Hotel</h4>
            <ul>
				<li>342 rooms, including 13 one-bedroom suites and 4 custom-designed luxury suites with breathtaking views</li>
				<li>Palm Suite (the hotel's Presidential suite) is complete with living and dining area, wet bar, outdoor patio, luxurious master bedroom, and signature Kohler bathroom fixtures </li>
				<li>Concierge Service</li>
				<li>Ocean Spa and Fitness Center - includes four treatment rooms for body and facial treatments</li>
				<li>Personalized fitness consultations and personal training</li>
				<li>Full-service beauty salon</li>
				<li>Valet parking</li>
				<li>17,000 square feet of function space accommodating groups up to 900</li>
            </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="infobox" id="amenities-infobox">
            <div id="the-rooms-infobox">
                <h4>The Rooms</h4>
                <ul>                    
					<li>24-hour room service</li>
					<li>Twice daily maid service</li>
					<li>Three telephones - two with dual lines and dataports</li>
					<li>Remote-control TV with HBO, CNN, ESPN, Disney Channel and Pay-Per-View</li>
					<li>Color TV in bathroom</li>
					<li>Plush waffle-cloth bathrobes</li>
					<li>Mini bar</li>
					<li>AM/FM clock radio with CD player</li>
					<li>Choice of newspaper with breakfast</li>
					<li>Make-up/shaving mirror, TV, hair dryer, scale and personal care items in bathrooms</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
    
            <div id="dining-lounges-infobox">	   
                <h4>Dining &amp; Lounges</h4>
                <ul>	
					<li>Ocean &amp; Vine - California-inspired "farm-to-table" cuisine with breathtaking views</li>
					<li>The Lounge ― Lobby bar and fireside lounge with panoramic views </li>
					<li>Poolside – Full-service poolside menu including sips, snacks and savory entrees</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="infobox" id="home-sweet-loews-infobox">
            <h4>Location</h4>
            <ul>              
				<li>20 minutes from Los Angeles International Airport</li>
				<li>Direct access to a magnificent California beach</li>
				<li>Short walk to Santa Monica Pier, cliff-top Palisades Park, and trendy Third Street Promenade</li>
				<li>Minutes from Beverly Hills, Century City and West LA</li>

            </ul>            
        </div>

